          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Commercial Register</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            Registration: HRB 17338<br />
            Registration Court: Amtsgericht Frankfurt (Oder)
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">VAT Identification Number</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">VAT ID pursuant to § 27 a German VAT Act: DE188194413</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Responsible for content pursuant to § 18 para. 2 MStV</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            Dr.-Ing. Jörn Budde<br />
            Silberberger Chaussee 14<br />
            15526 Bad Saarow
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
