          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            The European Commission provides a platform for online dispute resolution (ODR):
            <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr/" class="underline decoration-ink-line hover:text-blue" rel="noopener" target="_blank">https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr/</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Consumer dispute resolution</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            We are neither willing nor obliged to participate in dispute resolution proceedings before a consumer arbitration board.
